name: THE MOLE'S KING TOMB - Where that hole came from? (#04)
description:
This is the fourth part of the collection "The Mole's King Tomb", which will have 10 different Vinyl's.  9 of them will be separated tracks of the album, and the last one will be a special 1/1 Vinyl with the whole album itself in it!
the first collector the 1/1 NFT will receive a AUTOGRAPHED PHYSICAL TAPE OF THE ALBUM!
Since i still have two tapes left, i'm thinking about also doing a giveaway of the second one to the collectors of the separated album too, so stay tuned 👀
